PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_3_DESC: effective length (m) of taper in contact in axial direction disregarding (i.e. not subtracting) oil grooves and any part of the hub having a relief groove.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_4_DESC: The modulus of elasticity of the propeller hub.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_5_DESC: The modulus of elasticity of shaft.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_6_DESC: The ratio between DS and the mean outer diameter of propeller hub at the axial position corresponding to DS.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_7_DESC: The ratio between the inner diameter of the shaft and DS.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_10_DESC: Coefficient of linear expansion of shaft material.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_11_DESC: Coefficient of linear expansion of hub material.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_12_DESC: Min. yield strength of hub material.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_14_DESC: Ratio between shaft diameter and outer diameter of the propeller hub at thebig end of the cone.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_17_DESC: Diameter of the hub at half the length of the cone.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_19_DESC: Outer diameter of the hub on the larger diameter of the cone.
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_20_DESC: Internal diameter of the shaft (for hollow shafts).
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_FORMULA_0: The necessary surface pressure p (MPa) at 35°C[MPa]
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_FORMULA_1: For propeller without intermediate sleeve, corresponding required pull-up length (mm) at 35°C[MPa]
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_FORMULA_3: Corresponding maximum permissible pull-up length (mm) at 0°C
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_FORMULA_4: The minimum pull-up length (mm) at temperature t < 35°C [mm]
PROPELLER_DNV_LEDEND_LABEL_FORMULA_5: Corresponding maximum permissible pull-up length (mm) at temperature [mm]
